{"tid":1175561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逃犯條例資源整合","createTime":"2019-05-28T15:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T11:35:28.000Z","uid":41355,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"72a4262bc71b8af20ea644dcf0a9dba7ba5c39bb","tid":1175561,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15:41:54.000Z","msg":"小弟想整合逃犯條例既資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等連登仔宣傳／討論逃犯條例個陣唔駛搵POST搵得咁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n內容包括：<br />\n逃犯條例懶人包<br />\n文宣資源<br />\n街招／傳單資源<br />\n香港各界反應<br />\n國際社會回應<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10xqdrRbFtXzC-VFci-GBDcTqfCJ_J1xnKLLqQdyNzUs/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F10xqdrRbFtXzC-VFci-GBDcTqfCJ_J1xnKLLqQdyNzUs%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2Go8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=168d2185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10xqdrRbFtXzC-VFci-GBDcTqfCJ_J1xnKLLqQdyNzUs/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n但係個人力量有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家淨係整左一部分<br />\n好需要你幫手出一分力完善個document<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可以係呢度留言<br />\n或者係google sheet入面comment<br />\n我再加番資源入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07ea9f3150cc492e8335235a41d4956c53a6961","tid":1175561,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d3fa781d9344d37ea29805b815504c49e070794b","tid":1175561,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15:52:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"be1a4dff48a2c5baa2b12e058d3ec12b80dfe4e0","tid":1175561,"uid":68907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15: